OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778198576
OL,3,CInside the Met's antisemitism patrols
OL,5,FThe Met Police are putting more
OL,6,Fresources into protecting Jewish sites
OL,7,Fafter a spate of antisemitic attacks
OL,8,Fin London has left communities feeling
OL,9,Fvulnerable, ITV News Correspondent Sam
OL,10,FHolder reports
OL,12,FThe call comes in across the police
OL,13,Fradio.
OL,15,FA panic alarm was set off at a
OL,16,Fsynagogue building in Hendon.
OL,18,FSirens blaring, we weave through
OL,19,Ftraffic as quickly as possible.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778198576
OL,3,CInside the Met's antisemitism patrols
OL,5,FI'm out with one of the Metropolitan
OL,6,FPolice's new specialist patrols aimed
OL,7,Fat dealing with a rising tide of
OL,8,Fantisemitism.
OL,10,FThe patrols cover areas with large
OL,11,FJewish populations, like Golders
OL,12,FGreen, Hendon, Finchley and Edgware,
OL,13,Fand only respond to reports of terror
OL,14,Fattacks and hate crimes.
OL,16,FIt's a significant operation requiring
OL,17,F1,000 extra officer shifts a week,
OL,18,Fwhich relies on overtime and the
OL,19,Fredeployment of police officers from
OL,20,Fother parts of London.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778198576
OL,3,CInside the Met's antisemitism patrols
OL,5,FIt takes just under two minutes to
OL,6,Farrive at the scene. We are quickly
OL,7,Fjoined by three other police cars.
OL,9,FIn recent weeks, synagogues including
OL,10,FFinchley Reform and a former site in
OL,11,FStepney have been targeted in arson
OL,12,Fattacks.
OL,14,FThis call, however, is a false alarm.
OL,15,FA security alarm maintenance team had
OL,16,Faccidentally pressed a panic button
OL,17,Fwithout realising.
OL,19,FOfficers on the front line have seen
OL,20,Ffirst-hand the rise in antisemitism in
OL,21,Frecent weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778198576
OL,3,CInside the Met's antisemitism patrols
OL,5,FSince the arson attack on three
OL,6,Fambulances run by the Jewish charity
OL,7,FHatzola, which is when these patrols
OL,8,Fstarted, the number of weekly
OL,9,Fantisemitic attacks in London has
OL,10,Fdoubled.
OL,12,FMany incidents they handle do not get
OL,13,Fwidely reported, such as a recent
OL,14,Fattack on a Jewish man in a cafe in
OL,15,FGolders Green. The attacker then made
OL,16,Fa Nazi salute.
OL,18,F"From my experience, I've never seen
OL,19,Fso much of an increase in such a short
OL,20,Fspace of time," PC Zach Stimson, who
OL,21,Fresponded to the call, said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778198576
OL,3,CInside the Met's antisemitism patrols
OL,5,F"(It's a) really scary position to be
OL,6,Fin and I really feel for the
OL,7,Fcommunity," Sergeant Simon Vandepeer
OL,8,Ftold me.
OL,10,FAnother call comes across the police
OL,11,Fradio. Reports of a man acting
OL,12,Ferratically outside a Jewish primary
OL,13,Fschool.
OL,15,FOnce again, the blue lights are on,
OL,16,Fand we race to the scene.
OL,18,FThere has been particular concern
OL,19,Fabout Jewish schools being targeted.
OL,26,@mD@BpmmD@Ipn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778198576
OL,3,CInside the Met's antisemitism patrols
OL,5,FA school was amongst the locations
OL,6,Fthat two Iranian men were accused of
OL,7,Fspying on for Iran's government.
OL,9,FAnother school recently reported a
OL,10,Fsuspicious man standing outside and
OL,11,Ftaking photographs, while a third said
OL,12,Fthat students were nearly run over
OL,13,Fwhen a car mounted the pavement and
OL,14,Fdrove off.
OL,16,FIt takes us less than five minutes to
OL,17,Farrive at the primary school. Multiple
OL,18,Fother police cars and officers are
OL,19,Falready on the scene.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778198576
OL,3,CInside the Met's antisemitism patrols
OL,5,FThis time, it appears that the man,
OL,6,Fwho by now has jumped into the
OL,7,Fcourtyard of a Jewish learning centre,
OL,8,Fis suffering from a mental health
OL,9,Fcrisis but doesn't pose a threat.
OL,11,FBack on patrol, which involves
OL,12,Fcarrying out regular checks on
OL,13,Fparticularly high-risk sites like
OL,14,Fsynagogues, we drive past the three
OL,15,Fnew Hatzola ambulances, which replaced
OL,16,Fthose destroyed in an arson in March.
OL,18,FIt seems almost unbelievable that an
OL,19,Fambulance depot has to be regularly
OL,20,Fpatrolled.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778198576
OL,3,CInside the Met's antisemitism patrols
OL,5,FThe patrols are mostly about
OL,6,Freassurance for the Jewish community
OL,7,Fand providing a visible deterrent to
OL,8,Fthose thinking about carrying out
OL,9,Fattacks, but they have yielded results.
OL,11,F"Those additional assets and
OL,12,Fspecialist capabilities that we've had
OL,13,Fin Golders Green have been the units
OL,14,Fand teams that have identified some of
OL,15,Fthe incidents in the early stages of
OL,16,Fattack and have prevented those
OL,17,Fattacks becoming more serious", says
OL,18,FCommander James Conway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778198576
OL,3,CInside the Met's antisemitism patrols
OL,5,FSince they began, more than 70 people
OL,6,Fhave been arrested for religiously
OL,7,Fmotivated hate crimes.
OL,9,FAs we drive through Golders Green, we
OL,10,Fare flagged down by a van driver.
OL,12,FTwo young girls, around 13 years old,
OL,13,Fhave been accused of carrying out a
OL,14,Fcampaign of harassment against local
OL,15,FJewish children, including allegations
OL,16,Fthat they threatened to use a knife.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778198576
OL,3,CInside the Met's antisemitism patrols
OL,5,FWhen the girls spot the police van,
OL,6,Fthey scamper. For a minute or two, it
OL,7,Fseems like they've disappeared, but
OL,8,Feventually they are found hiding
OL,9,Fbehind a bin.
OL,11,FFirst at the scene was Yonathan El
OL,12,FKouby, a volunteer with Shomrim, who
OL,13,Facts as a sort of security force to
OL,14,Fprotect the Jewish community.
OL,16,FHe was also the first person on the
OL,17,Fscene during the Golders Green terror
OL,18,Fattack last week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778198576
OL,3,CInside the Met's antisemitism patrols
OL,5,F"Thinking back about it, for sure
OL,6,Fyou'd say that was a scary thing,
OL,7,Fespecially when the person came
OL,8,Ftowards me with a knife," he said.
OL,10,F"It could have been me, luckily it
OL,11,Fwasn't. These are things you
OL,12,Fdefinitely worry about. You want to
OL,13,Fmake sure you protect the community."
OL,15,FDespite experiencing something that
OL,16,Fwould have left plenty of people
OL,17,Ftraumatised, he was out volunteering
OL,18,Fthe next day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778198576
OL,3,CInside the Met's antisemitism patrols
OL,5,FThe Metropolitan Police told me they
OL,6,Fhave a good working relationship with
OL,7,Fboth Shomrim and the Community
OL,8,FSecurity Trust (CST), another security
OL,9,Fforce which handles the protection of
OL,10,Fsynagogues and other Jewish sites.
OL,12,FVolunteers from both Shomrim and CST
OL,13,Fwill often be the first to be alerted
OL,14,Fto an incident and then liaise with
OL,15,Fthe police, depending on the severity.
OL,17,FThe two girls are marched home to
OL,18,Ftheir parents and now face further
OL,19,Finterviews at the local police station.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778198576
OL,3,CInside the Met's antisemitism patrols
OL,5,FIf it wasn't for the patrol driving
OL,6,Fpast, it is unlikely they would have
OL,7,Fbeen caught.
OL,9,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,10,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,11,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,12,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,14,FIn reality, this level of policing is
OL,15,Funsustainable. It is supposed to be a
OL,16,Ftemporary response to the rise in anti-
OL,17,FSemitism, but, as attacks continue, it
OL,18,Fisn't clear when it will end.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778198576
OL,3,CInside the Met's antisemitism patrols
OL,5,FAround #18 million of the #25 million
OL,6,Fadditional police funding from the
OL,7,Fgovernment to tackle antisemitism has
OL,8,Fgone to the Metropolitan Police. The
OL,9,Fvast majority of Jewish people in
OL,10,FBritain live in a few areas of London.
OL,12,FThe Met have also announced a new
OL,13,Fdedicated Community Protection Team,
OL,14,Finitially made up of 100 extra
OL,15,Fofficers, which they say will be
OL,16,F"intelligence-led" and will be focused
OL,17,Fon protecting the Jewish community.
OL,19,FFurther details are currently being
OL,20,Fworked out.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778198576
OL,3,CInside the Met's antisemitism patrols
OL,5,FFor many, though, in areas like
OL,6,FGolders Green, it isn't extra police
OL,7,Fofficers that they want.
OL,9,FWe are stopped in the street by
OL,10,FDanielle, right next to where the
OL,11,FGolders Green attack took place.
OL,13,FShe echoes what I've heard time and
OL,14,Ftime again from people in the Jewish
OL,15,Fcommunity, that the police response
OL,16,Fisn't dealing with the root causes of
OL,17,Fantisemitism.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778198576
OL,3,CInside the Met's antisemitism patrols
OL,5,FDanielle wants the Met to focus on
OL,6,Ffirmer policing of Palestine marches
OL,7,Fand other protests, which have seen
OL,8,Frepeated usage of anti-Semitic
OL,9,Flanguage.
OL,11,F"I find it frustrating that they are
OL,12,Fcoming and trying to protect us when
OL,13,Freally they should be clamping down on
OL,14,Fthe source of the problem, which is
OL,15,Fthe hate speech," she said.
OL,17,F"I don't want to have to have police
OL,18,Fat our schools, shops and places of
OL,19,Fworship".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
